### Project Description

It is our hope this helps tell the water story in some small way. This project highlights the following
 areas:
 
 Ground water well data
 Evapotranspiration
 Precipitation 
 Reservoir Storage 
 Critical Habitat loss due to Drought
 Steelhead and Stream Flow
